---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato and Fresh Mozzarella Focaccia with Arugula, Olive and Tomato Salad
description: Making bread has never been this easy! No-fuss focaccia made with pizza dough is one of our fave hacks at HelloFresh! Sun-dried tomato pesto topped with fresh mozzarella and Parm isn't just gorgeous to look at, it's a taste revelation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/focaccia-aux-tomates-sechees-et-a-la-mozzarella-fraiche-54a51433.jpg
